Proposed Solution:
1) Steps:
- X corresponds to the inner disk r ≤ 4: area = π(4^2) = 16π.
- Y corresponds to the annulus 4 < r ≤ 6: area = π(6^2 − 4^2) = 20π.
- Z corresponds to the annulus 6 < r ≤ 7: area = π(7^2 − 6^2) = 13π.
